evidence converter with a custom evidence converter that performs no evidence conversion.
Procedure
1. Create a custom disabled evidence converter which extends the default evidence converter
that you are disabling. The custom converter needs to override the convert() method so that no
evidence is converted.
For example, see this custom Annual Tax Return external evidence converter that contains an
